## Sample Fidelity Checklist

| Step | Did I do it? |
|------|:---:|
| Gave 10-minute advance warning            | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Gave 5-minute advance warning             | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Started timer for bedtime routine         | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Followed visual schedule for routine steps | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Offered limited choices during routine     | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Ignored escape behaviors (did not chase)   | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Did not negotiate or argue                 | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Provided sticker/praise for compliance     | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Honored bedtime pass if used               | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
| Recorded data in journal                   | ☐ Yes  ☐ No |
</Markdown>
</IntakeGate>


